<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Python on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/python/</link><description>Recent content in Python on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/python/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] R Keras / TensorFlow Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/r-keras-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/r-keras-error/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Keras/TensorFlow errors in R occur when the R interface to Python-based Keras fails. This can happen during installation, configuration, or model training and inference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Python environment not properly configured&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;TensorFlow version mismatch with Keras&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;GPU driver or CUDA issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Memory exhaustion during training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invalid model architecture or tensor shapes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# WRONG: Missing Python configuration&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;library&lt;/span&gt;(keras)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;model &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;keras_model_sequential&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Error: Python not found&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CORRECT: Configure Python first&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;library&lt;/span&gt;(reticulate)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;use_python&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/usr/bin/python3&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;library&lt;/span&gt;(keras)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# WRONG: Version mismatch&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;install_keras&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Installs latest, may conflict&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CORRECT: Pin compatible versions&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;library&lt;/span&gt;(reticulate)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;virtualenv_create&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;keras-env&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;virtualenv_install&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;keras-env&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, packages &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;tensorflow==2.12.0&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;keras==2.12.0&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;use_virtualenv&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;keras-env&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# WRONG: Training with incompatible tensor shapes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;model &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;keras_model_sequential&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;%&amp;gt;%&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;layer_dense&lt;/span&gt;(units &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;32&lt;/span&gt;, input_shape &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;)) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;%&amp;gt;%&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;layer_dense&lt;/span&gt;(units &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fit&lt;/span&gt;(model, x_train, y_train) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Error if dimensions mismatch&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CORRECT: Verify shapes before training&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cat&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;x_train shape:&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;dim&lt;/span&gt;(x_train), &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;\n&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cat&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;y_train shape:&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;dim&lt;/span&gt;(y_train), &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;\n&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 1: Install Keras properly&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;install.packages&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;keras&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;library&lt;/span&gt;(keras)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;install_keras&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 2: Check TensorFlow version&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;library&lt;/span&gt;(tensorflow)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;tf&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;constant&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello TensorFlow&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 3: GPU memory management&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;library&lt;/span&gt;(keras)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;config &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; tf&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ConfigProto&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;config&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;gpu_options&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;allow_growth &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TRUE&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;session &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; tf&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Session&lt;/span&gt;(config &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; config)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;k_set_session&lt;/span&gt;(session)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/error-in-library/"&gt;error-in-library&lt;/a&gt; — package load failed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/error-in-install.packages/"&gt;error-in-install.packages&lt;/a&gt; — installation issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/error-in-source/"&gt;error-in-source&lt;/a&gt; — sourcing errors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>ImportError: cannot import name 'X'</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flask/import-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flask/import-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when Python cannot find the specified name (function, class, or variable) in the module you are trying to import. In Flask projects it frequently happens with circular imports or when referencing renamed/removed symbols.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Circular import between application modules (e.g. &lt;code&gt;models.py&lt;/code&gt; importing from &lt;code&gt;app.py&lt;/code&gt; which imports from &lt;code&gt;models.py&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The name was renamed or removed in the target module&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Typo in the imported name&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The module was not installed or is not on &lt;code&gt;sys.path&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Break circular imports by moving shared code into a separate module or using lazy imports:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>